ActRoyal Canadian Mint Act
SubjectIssuance of two $2 circulation coins with a design commemorating the 75th anniversary of the end of the Second World War
PrecisOrder Authorizing the ISSUANCE of two $2 circulation coins with a design commemorating the 75th anniversary of the end of the Second World War in order to foster remembrance and serve as tangible keepsakes of the contributions and sacrifices of those who served Canada.
